---
const personalImageAlt = "Agustin Del Monte";
---

<article
	class="relative flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-8 md:gap-12 md:flex-row group"
>
	<!-- Efecto de brillo de fondo -->
	<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500/5 to-purple-500/5 rounded-3xl blur-3xl opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500"></div>

	<div
		class="relative z-10 space-y-6 text-gray-300 [&>p>strong]:font-semibold [&>p>strong]:font-mono text-pretty order-2 md:order-1 opacity-0 animate-fade-in"
	>
		<p class="text-base leading-relaxed">
			Mi nombre es <strong
				class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-cyan-300"
				>Agustín Del Monte</strong
			>.
		</p>

		<p class="text-base leading-relaxed">
			Soy <strong class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-cyan-300">
				Técnico Universitario en Programación</strong
			>  con perfil Full Stack con experiencia en desarrollo de aplicaciones web, manejo de bases de datos, consumo de APIs, diseño web, desarrollo backend, integración de servicios y  tecnologias modernas.  Orientado a buenas prácticas, trabajo en equipo y aprendizaje continuo.

		</p>

		<p class="text-base leading-relaxed border-l-4 border-blue-500/40 pl-4 py-2 bg-blue-500/5 rounded-r-lg">
			graduado de la Universidad Tecnológica Nacional en Mendoza, Argentina.
		</p>
	</div>

	<div class="order-1 md:order-2 relative opacity-0 animate-fade-in-delay ml-0 mr-auto md:mx-0 md:mr-20">
		<!-- Efecto de anillo decorativo -->
		<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-purple-500 rounded-2xl opacity-20 blur-xl scale-105 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500"></div>
		
		<div class="relative z-10 w-40 h-52 sm:w-48 sm:h-64 md:w-52 md:h-60 overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border-2 border-white/10 shadow-2xl group-hover:scale-105 group-hover:border-blue-400/30 transition-all duration-500">
			<img
				src="/Projects/foto.png"
				alt={personalImageAlt}
				class="w-full h-full object-cover"
				style="object-position: center center;"
			/>
		</div>
	</div>
</article>

<style>
	@keyframes fade-in {
		0% {
			opacity: 0;
			transform: translateY(1.5rem);
		}
		100% {
			opacity: 1;
			transform: translateY(0);
		}
	}

	.animate-fade-in {
		animation: fade-in 0.8s ease-out forwards;
	}

	.animate-fade-in-delay {
		animation: fade-in 0.8s ease-out 0.3s forwards;
	}
</style>